casebody.data:
No. 586. City of St. Charles, Petitioner, v. Charles A. Stookey. February 24, 1908. Mr. Shepard Barclay and Mr. Thomas T. Fauntleroy for petitioner. Mr. Charles Nagel for respondent.

Petition for a writ of certiorari to the United States Circuit Court of Appeals for the Eighth Circuit denied.
